Package: CodeExtractoR
Type: Package
Title: Extract Code snippets from PDF files, primarily from RJournal
Encoding: UTF-8
Version: 1.0
Author: Paweł Morgen
Maintainer: Paweł Morgen <seriousmorgen@protonmail.com>
Description: A wrapper around API converting pdf to html file, using pdf2htmlex. 
              The downloaded file is then searched for code snippets, based on their unique font.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: stringi,
         httr,
         tools,
         rex
Suggests: knitr,
          rmarkdown,
          testthat,
          httptest
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://MrDomani.github.io/CodeExtractoR/, https://github.com/MrDomani/CodeExtractoR
BugReports: https://github.com/MrDomani/CodeExtractoR/issues
